static/621a6b0d10e4253193ddebe7de764e8d/3ac88/merge-layers.jpg 1260w,\n/static/621a6b0d10e4253193ddebe7de764e8d/38f6f/merge-layers.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Here we have combined layers in one layer.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/00291/final-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.9620253164557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, final-2\"\n        title=\"Photopea, final-2\"\n        src=\"/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/828fb/final-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/ff44c/final-2.jpg 158w,\n/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/a6688/final-2.jpg 315w,\n/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/828fb/final-2.jpg 630w,\n/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/0ede0/final-2.jpg 945w,\n/static/66a8e1839188f54256c60da2976b3d91/00291/final-2.jpg 1209w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>When you follow the above steps then it will combine layers in photopea.</p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to combine layers in photopea?","tags":["Photopea"],"date":"Sep